com.pos.device.icc

Interface IccReaderCallback


  • public interface IccReaderCallback
    Interface for monitoring the state of searching Ic Card result.
    Author:
    Created by Paddy on 2016/9/21 09:08

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int READER_CLOSED
      The IC Card reader has closed during searching.
      static int SUCCESS
      Search the IC Card successfully
      static int TIMEOUT_ERROR
      Search IC Card timeout
      static int USER_CANCEL
      Be canceled by user during searching IC Card.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onSearchResult(int result)

      • onSearchResult

        void onSearchResult(int result)
        This method be called automatically when searched the IC Card, canceled by user ,searched card timeout or reader be closed.
